      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Available is a 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-tuned limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Significant mechanical stewardship is evident, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of this platform. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally crisp. A mechanically sound, high-performance icon ready for the canyons.",
